                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per turn; <strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within the soulbound ruin uses an action with the move trait. <strong>Effect</strong> The soulbound ruin reacts violently to stop the creature's movement, shooting spikes, throwing bricks, or otherwise impeding the target. The target must succeed at a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"35\" data-pf2-label=\"Impede DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Reflex</span> save or fall prone</p>"
